Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The World Series
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407jmy
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 16 Oct 1977
The US fascination with their 'World Series', the baseball champion play-offs. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.